      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH ON DEMAND (6) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (22.74) in a Mix 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Will find this more suitable and can atone. MUSCOVITE MICA (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 22.39 beating DON'T CRY MAMA. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. WEBLEC JEWEL (3) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage second, beaten 0.8 lengths (22.20) at this track in a Mix 5 over 390m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to be in the finish again. MONKEY PANTS (2) is worth including after a top-three finish at this track and distance most recently.",
